+# Scoop requires a windows archive
+
+The Scoop pipe requires a Windows build and archive.
+
+The archive should not be in `binary` format.
+
+For instance, this won't work:
+
+```yaml
+archives:
+- format: binary
+```
+
+
+But this would:
+
+```yaml
+archives:
+- format: zip
+```
